29#ifndef ZFS_ITER_H
30#define ZFS_ITER_H
31
32#ifdef __cplusplus
33extern "C" {
34#endif
35
36typedef struct zfs_sort_column {
37 struct zfs_sort_column *sc_next;
38 struct zfs_sort_column *sc_last;
39 zfs_prop_t sc_prop;
40 char *sc_user_prop;
41 boolean_t sc_reverse;
42} zfs_sort_column_t;
43
44#define ZFS_ITER_RECURSE (1 << 0)
45#define ZFS_ITER_ARGS_CAN_BE_PATHS (1 << 1)
46#define ZFS_ITER_PROP_LISTSNAPS (1 << 2)
47#define ZFS_ITER_DEPTH_LIMIT (1 << 3)
48#define ZFS_ITER_RECVD_PROPS (1 << 4)
49#define ZFS_ITER_SIMPLE (1 << 5)
50#define ZFS_ITER_LITERAL_PROPS (1 << 6)
51
52int zfs_for_each(int, char **, int options, zfs_type_t,
53 zfs_sort_column_t *, zprop_list_t **, int, zfs_iter_f, void *);
54int zfs_add_sort_column(zfs_sort_column_t **, const char *, boolean_t);
55void zfs_free_sort_columns(zfs_sort_column_t *);
56boolean_t zfs_sort_only_by_name(const zfs_sort_column_t *);
57
58#ifdef __cplusplus
59}
60#endif
61
62#endif /* ZFS_ITER_H */
